{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id903a3a6b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3403"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3403"},"text":"§ 3403.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Supplemental authorization of economic support for Egypt","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There is authorized to be appropriated to the President to carry out chapter 4 of part II of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2346"},"text":"22 U.S.C. 2346","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], $300,000,000 for the fiscal year 1979 for Egypt, in addition to amounts otherwise authorized to be appropriated for such chapter for the fiscal year 1979. The amounts appropriated pursuant to this section may be made available until expended."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id903a3a6c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/35/s5"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–35, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-07-20"},"text":"July 20, 1979","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/93/91"},"text":"93 Stat. 91","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id903a3a6d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id903a3a6e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id903a3a6f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Foreign Assistance Act of 1961, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/195"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–195","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-09-04"},"text":"Sept. 4, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/424"},"text":"75 Stat. 424","children":[],"tail":". Chapter 4 of part II of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 is classified to part IV (§ 2346 et seq.) of subchapter II of chapter 32 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2151"},"text":"section 2151 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
